== Index an ontology ==
(% class="half" %)(((
{{html wiki=false clean=false}}
&lt;form class="xform solr-admin" action='' method="post"&gt;
&lt;dl&gt;
&lt;dt&gt;
&lt;label for="ontology-url"&gt;Ontology&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;span class="xHint"&gt;The URL of a file containing the ontology you wish to index in &lt;a href="http://www.bioontology.org/wiki/index.php/OboInOwl:Main_Page" rel="_blank"&gt;OBO format&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/dt&gt;
&lt;dd class="mandatory"&gt;&lt;input type="text" name="url" id="ontology-url" value="http://compbio.charite.de/svn/hpo/trunk/src/ontology/human-phenotype-ontology.obo"/&gt;&lt;/dd&gt;
&lt;dt&gt;
&lt;label for="ontology-fields"&gt;Fields to index&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;span class="xHint"&gt;A comma separated list on fields to be indexed for this term (e.g. "id,name,def,synonym,is_a"). Alternatively, you can choose to boost the weight of some fields, as follows: "id:50,name,def,synonym,is_a:0.1". If no fields are specified, all the fields in each term will be indexed, with the default weight 1.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/dt&gt;
&lt;dd&gt;&lt;input type="text" name="fields" id="ontology-fields" value=""/&gt;&lt;/dd&gt;
&lt;/dl&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;span class="buttonwrapper"&gt;&lt;input class="button" type="submit" name="actionindex" value="Start indexing"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;
{{/html}}

{{warning}}Indexing may take a while, please be patient.{{/warning}}

)))


